# Claude Code session worktrees. Each one carries its own checked-out copy of
# biome.json — with vcs.useIgnoreFile on, gitignoring this keeps Biome's project
# discovery from treating those copies as competing nested root configs ("Found a
# nested root configuration" errors breaking `bun run lint` from the main tree).
.claude/worktrees/
